Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.99,0:00:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.16,0:00:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\N this world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone is in search of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly \Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:44.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jitto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:44.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
