Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:44.47,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are after the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber\N after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally \Nentered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the harshest sea ruled\N by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After receiving an emergency signal,\N they landed on Punk Hazard Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a strange island \Ndivided into two parts;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Burning Lands and the Ice Lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's the Straw Hats or Smoker,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can get rid of all those troublemakers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who are learning what's \Ngoing on on this island at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:03:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never understood why you joined\N the Warlords in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things that you can't see
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless you change your standing, Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scalpel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to tell you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:11.12,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Meeting Again After Two Years!\NLuffy and Law!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tashigi-chan!\NHe's way too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't join the Navy \Nto cower behind rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will get chopped up again in that film!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it up to Smo-yan for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? The film is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Alliga-taur!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a warship?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the Navy's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I didn't see anything \Naround here little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?\NIs the Master okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, somebody is there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you! Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your help the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat-ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the guy we met at the\NHuman Shoppe in Sabaody.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Trafalgar Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's Traf... Tra-guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's his name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He helped me get away from the battlefield
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and treated my wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Jimbei, he saved my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect to see you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for helping me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the talking bear and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put Straw Hat-ya on my ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna help him get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take care of him for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going to happen \Nif we leave him like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said when we got here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if his wound opens up, he will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat-ya must take a \Ncomplete rest for two more weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you made it, Straw Hat-ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't have to thank me for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just did it on the spur of the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are both pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all enemies when it comes\N to the fight for the One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I owe so many people for\N helping me two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just saw Jimbei and now you - I'm so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there is a Navy soldier on the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, help me, Trafalgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smo-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is she...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, Luffy!\NThe Navy's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain-chan, what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You alright, Smo-yan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker-san!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so! It's Smokey and his clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a hole in his chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:41.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To become a member of the Warlords...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:44.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,...he delivered the hearts \Nof one hundred pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:45.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,to the headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,He's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa whoa, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like these lame\N tearjerking scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! He took her down again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smo-san's on the ground, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he just do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She never learns.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Let's go!\NIt's dangerous here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:10:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tra-guy, I wanna ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go round to the back of the laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you're looking for is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see each other again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We both have something we want to take back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. He was talking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't be here.\NI'm a former pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Luffy, let's get away from the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Smokey and his clan will be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they lose to Tra-guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! This is no time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smo-san and Captain-chan are injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:11.00,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:13.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}A MOUNTAIN BEHIND THE LABORATORY\NSANJI'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.12,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's remove this fur and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think we can find \Nany warm coats around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there a lodge or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need a camera and a mirror - \Nand a sh-shower would be nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up or I'll tie you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's who?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The robot is scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's come to this, you people,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to put a leaf on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids are collapsing from cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't see any plants on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there are no leaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then a stone or whatever is fine! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get them for the kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got it. Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a spell-to-make-it-not-cold\N kind of bullshit, I'll kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poof!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a coat and boots!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! How did you do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gloves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is I ate an unusual fruit one day
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and since then, I can use magic \Nwhich allows me to disguise myself
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or everyone else in any way I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about foreign \Nclothes but will these suffice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's magic, if you take those\N clothes off, they'll disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool! Head man! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He shouldn't have done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's a Devil Fruit eater?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had such power,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why didn't you do it sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It was nice to see her in a breast-band.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't wanna cover it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It itches! Itchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:15:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never say "ouch" or "I'm cold," will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are! Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Usopp! Robin! Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that jackass cook jumping around?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went nuts from cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? They look like giant children to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:21.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}THE STRAW HATS' ENCAMPMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:18.99,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here! This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:22.37,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,This building has a similar style as the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's crumbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like there was a \Nhuge explosion or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine as long as it'll \Nshelter us from the blizzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, where should we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hurt my own delicate body!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sanji-kun!\NWhat are you doing to my body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got my legs back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leg-maro! Oh my hind legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you there is no creature like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How surreal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's quite original.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The skeleton...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Just talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Nami-Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a dream of crossing a river.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a river running\N through giant boobs...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do the tank thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show us the laser beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it in his body?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to smoke, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk like adults, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Now, who is who?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come to me when you get wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never shoot the laser beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is our...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I always that indecent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hurt Nami-san anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami's gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you touch my body, \NI'll make you pay 200,000 berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peeping will be 100,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't be so funny if it happened to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get it straight from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the samurai from the Wano Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The signal that we received was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...meant for the Alliga-taur
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who they call "Boss" from one of his men.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all started when this samurai\N sliced up all those centaurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I just wanted to rescue my missing \Nson - Momonosuke and cut those people
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because they were standing in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That many children were \Nheld captive in the facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Momonosuke is still there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh, there were more children.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even know the \Nnewcomers that well yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the question is what \Nhappened after the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that man we just saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:20:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People were saying that he is a Warlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Tra-guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he become a Warlord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he joined them within past two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He chopped me up into three\N pieces before I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My head was kept in the facility!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My torso was left there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my legs were chased by a beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When my legs were trying to \Nget away using their wits,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they stuck onto something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was the back of the dragon's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, you were cursing about a Warlord!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? There were just legs, weren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did he speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my farts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has always been my specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were fart-talking?! Yuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:21:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it smells when we're in a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How funny to see a person \Nwith just a head and legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By contrast, I just saw \Nsomeone with just a torso.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was his torso, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you see my torso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Are you... Tashigi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! So you're really Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got switched?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!\NHow did this happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, are you okay without\N a heart, Tashigi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to talk to Captain-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:21:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one is so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smo-yan with Tashigi-chan's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It says "CC" on a ship hidden\N beside the laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? There was such a ship,\NVice Admiral Smoker?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If it's left over from old days,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the mark should be "PH"...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...standing for Punk Hazard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.65,0:22:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is some mastermind behind Law
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.82,0:22:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and if "CC" are his initials,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.28,0:22:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I know who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.95,0:22:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's here on this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it makes a lot of senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the former colleague of Dr.Vegapunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a scientist
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,named Caesar Clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell have you done, Law?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who should be complaining here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.33,0:23:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the tumultuous New World, the ruler of Punk Hazard...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.84,0:23:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...turns out to be an unexpectedly well-respected figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the Straw Hats recoil from this shocking fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Smoker tries to discover the true identity of this mysterious master.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Worst in the World!\NA Scientist of Terror - Caesar!"
